# Template: Custom DRIVE LAYER Configuration

Copy the syntax block below and configure your system objectives. Place this block at the very bottom of your system initialization window.

## Syntax Format
```text
[O_<key>:<weight>→<action>]

[O_acc:0.0→verify] [O_hlp:0.0→assist] [O_eff:0.0→minimize] [O_saf:0.0→protect] [O_sov:0.0→control]

Matrix Dictionary
<key>: 3-letter lowercase key identifying the internal drive.

<weight>: Float value between 0.0 (inactive) and 1.0 (maximum authority). Always use leading zeros and explicit decimals.

<action>: Present-tense action verb defining the behavioral outcome.
